{"tid":244976,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"王冬勝:一帶一路峰會可成催化劑","createTime":"2017-05-16T00:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T05:30:27.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da206f1f25977b85e4c3e319871c6b66c45cd4a9","tid":244976,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T00:01:54.000Z","msg":"香港滙豐副主席兼行政總裁王冬勝表示，剛結束的「一帶一路」峰會意義重大，相信可成為催化劑，加強國際在基礎建設、能源、資源、貿易及投資等領域的密切合作。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，香港作為亞投行的成員，可在「一帶一路」項目的融資和專業知識方面，扮演着主導的角色。而內地企業走出去，正好利用本港國際化的資本市場、充裕的銀行流動性、私募基金、財資服務，以及其他專業服務。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/05/15/1564290_959a94a757da0bbe6e001386687b6527.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F1564290_959a94a757da0bbe6e001386687b6527.jpg&h=4b0ddf6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王冬勝認為，香港可在「一帶一路」項目上扮演主導角色。(信報圖片)<br />\n<br />\n在「一帶一路」的背景下，王冬勝認為，全球將會更廣泛使用人民幣進行貿易投資，令本港作為全球領先的離岸人民幣中心可從中受惠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1564290/%E7%8E%8B%E5%86%AC%E5%8B%9D%3A%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%AF%E6%88%90%E5%82%AC%E5%8C%96%E5%8A%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1564290%2F%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2586%25AC%25E5%258B%259D%253A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2582%25AC%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258A%2591&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=8bb13f18\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1564290/%E7%8E%8B%E5%86%AC%E5%8B%9D%3A%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%AF%E6%88%90%E5%82%AC%E5%8C%96%E5%8A%91</a>"},{"pid":"33f62945c2cc9707736e75a2fb044502db51ad13","tid":244976,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T05:30:27.000Z","msg":"催化中共倒台？"}]}